oai_dc:dc.dc:title: First Preparatory Class Medal
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Medals
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Christian Brothers College student, George Fossick, received this medal for being a member of the First Preparatory Class in 1885-1886. Fossick attended CBC from 1883-1886.
